sparql_query_kg2:
 Based on the given context, the SPARQL query for KG2 (Wikidata) to retrieve a list of soccer clubs that play in the Bundesliga is as follows:

```sparql
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE {
  ?uri wdt:P31 wd:Q476028 ;
        wdt:P118 wd:Q82595 .
}
```

This query selects distinct URIs (?uri) where the entity is an instance of a soccer club (wdt:P31 wd:Q476028) and plays in the Bundesliga (wdt:P118 wd:Q82595).

