sparql_query_kg2:
 Given the information provided, here is the SPARQL query for KG2 (Wikidata) to find the last movie with Alec Guinness:

```sparql
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE {
  ?uri wdt:P31 wd:Q11424 ;
        wdt:P161 wd:Q103894 ;
        wdt:P577 ?date .
} ORDER BY DESC(?date) LIMIT 1
```

This query uses the Wikidata prefixes and identifiers for Film (Q11424), starring (P161), Alec Guinness (Q103894), and releaseDate (P577) to retrieve the most recent movie in which Alec Guinness starred.

