The DBpedia query is:
```sparql
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lou_Reed> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/genre> ?uri }
```

Using the entity and relation mappings provided:
```json
