        <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/ideology> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pro-Europeanism>
}
```

We can map the DBpedia properties and resources to their Wikidata equivalents using the provided mappings:

- `http://dbpedia.org/ontology/PoliticalParty` maps to `http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q7278`.
- `http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country` maps to `http://www.wikidata.org/entity/P17`.
- `http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece` maps to `http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q41`.
- `http://dbpedia.org/ontology/ideology` maps to `http://www.wikidata.org/entity/P1142`.
- `http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pro-Europeanism` maps to `http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q3781399`.

The corresponding Wikidata query is:
```sparql
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

