### DBpedia Query:
```sparql
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE {
  ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/SoccerPlayer> ;
        <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta>
}
```

### Wikidata Query:
```sparql
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE {
  ?uri wdt:P31 wd:Q937857 ;
        wdt:P19 wd:Q233 .
}
```

### Final Wikidata SPARQL Query:
```sparql
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE {
  ?uri wdt:P31 wd:Q937857 ;
        wdt:P19 wd:Q233 .
}
```

This query selects distinct URIs of soccer players (`wdt:P31 wd:Q937857`) who were born in Malta (`wdt:P19 wd:Q233`).

